snippet.title: Revenot New Update! All about style!
snippet.description:
On this update I'm bringing you a huge update on the graphics of the game, and, believe or not, also in the performance!
New visuals to render the game like a cartoon, new skies and major changes on the exploration map will make Revenot look like a new game!
Let me know in the social media what you think about this update!

Oh, and of course, I've fixed some bugs as well.
